79633>>>// This code is part of VDF GUIdance
79633>>>// Visit us @ http://www.vdf-guidance.com
79633>>>// e-Mail us @ info@vdf-guidance.com
79633>>>// VDF GUIdance is a mutual project of
79633>>>// Frank Vandervelpen - Vandervelpen Systems and
79633>>>// Wil van Antwerpen  - Antwise Solutions
