80377>>>//****************************************************************************
80377>>>// $Module type: Class
80377>>>// $Module name: cDbUpdateFunctionLibrary
80377>>>// $Author     : Nils G. Svedmyr, RDC Tools International, <mailto:support@rdctools.com>
80377>>>// Web-site    : http://www.rdctools.com
80377>>>// Created     : 2014-09-05 @ 09:50 (Military date format: YY-MM-DD)
80377>>>//
80377>>>// Description : The class consists of a function library for database manipulations, aka make changes to a database.
80377>>>//               It has top level functions that uses the DataFlex db API, _but_ also specialized
80377>>>//               functions to make db changes to Sql databases with the DAW & Mertech drivers,
80377>>>//               with the help of Sql-scripts.
80377>>>//
80377>>>// $Rev History:
80377>>>//    2014-09-05  Module header created
80377>>>//   
80377>>>//****************************************************************************
80377>>>Use cApplication.pkg
