81424>>>>>>>
81424>>>>>>>    Procedure SeedDataSources
81426>>>>>>>        Local String  sDriver
81426>>>>>>>        Local String  sVoid
81426>>>>>>>        Local Integer iRetval
81426>>>>>>>
81426>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID To sDriver
81427>>>>>>>        If (sDriver <> "") ;            Call_Driver 0 sDRiver Function CLI_INITDATASOURCES Callback 0 Passing sVoid sVoid SQL_FETCH_ALL Result iRetval
81434>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SeedDataSources
81435>>>>>>>
81435>>>>>>>
