81435>>>>>>>    Function DataSources Returns String
81437>>>>>>>        Local String  sDriver
81437>>>>>>>        Local String  sDataSource
81437>>>>>>>        Local String  sDescription
81437>>>>>>>        Local Integer iLength
81437>>>>>>>        Local Integer iRetval
81437>>>>>>>
81437>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID To sDriver
81438>>>>>>>        If (sDriver <> "") Begin
81440>>>>>>>            Move 8192 To iLength
81441>>>>>>>            Move (Repeat(" ", iLength)) To sDataSource
81442>>>>>>>            Move (Repeat(" ", iLength)) To sDescription
81443>>>>>>>            Call_Driver 0 sDRiver Function CLI_DATASOURCES Callback 0 Passing sDataSource sDescription iLength Result iRetval
81448>>>>>>>        End
81448>>>>>>>>
81448>>>>>>>
81448>>>>>>>        If (sDataSource <> "" Or sDescription <> "") ;            Function_Return (sDataSource + "," +  sDescription)
81451>>>>>>>        Else ;            Function_Return ""
81453>>>>>>>    End_Function// DataSources
81454>>>>>>>
81454>>>>>>>End_Class // cODBCHandler
