81493>>>>>>>// The DDF owner is required when Pervasive.SQL security is turned on.
81493>>>>>>>// The DDF owner is equal to the password of the Master user in Pervasive.SQL
81493>>>>>>>// This command overwrites the DDF_OWNER setting in DFBTRDRV.INT
