82100>>>>>//****************************************************************************
82100>>>>>// $Module type: Class
82100>>>>>// $Module name: cSQLConnectionHandler.pkg
82100>>>>>// $Author     : Nils G. Svedmyr, RDC Tools International, <mailto:support@rdctools.com>
82100>>>>>// Web-site    : http://www.rdctools.com
82100>>>>>// Created     : 2015-08-11 @ 16:02 (Military date format: YY-MM-DD)
82100>>>>>//
82100>>>>>// Description : A handler class for using CLI connection ID's to login to a database server.
82100>>>>>//
82100>>>>>// $Rev History:
82100>>>>>//    2015-08-11  Module header created
82100>>>>>//    2016-09-26  Changed name of the objecthandle from ghoCreateConnectionID to ghoSQLConnectionHandler.
82100>>>>>//                Added a new structure for passing connection data back & forth.
82100>>>>>//                Added better error handling.
82100>>>>>//                Added a decompose message for the connection string.
82100>>>>>//    2017-01-09  Added support for Mertech drivers
82100>>>>>//                Big overhaul to comply better with "Managed Connections" (DF 19)
82100>>>>>//                These changes make the class compatible with DFConnId.ini (can read/write DAW connection ini-files)
82100>>>>>//    2017-02-12  Reworked the whole connection property interface.
82100>>>>>//                Now there is one struct property that is the at cencter of a connection.
82100>>>>>//****************************************************************************
