82100>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver is a cObject
82101>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
82103>>>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
82105>>>>>>>>>        Property String psDriverID DATAFLEX_ID
82106>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure 
82107>>>>>>>>>    
82107>>>>>>>>>    Function ServerKeyword Returns String
82109>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return CS_SQLIniDSNKeyword
82110>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82111>>>>>>>>>    
82111>>>>>>>>>    Function ConstructConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns String
82113>>>>>>>>>        String sConnect
82113>>>>>>>>>        
82113>>>>>>>>>        Move (sConnect * ServerKeyword(Self) + "=" + sServer) to sConnect
82114>>>>>>>>>        If (sDatabase <> "") Begin
82116>>>>>>>>>            Move (sConnect * ";" + CS_SQLIniDatabaseKeyword + "=" + sDatabase) to sConnect
82117>>>>>>>>>        End
82117>>>>>>>>>>
82117>>>>>>>>>        If (bTrusted = True) Begin
82119>>>>>>>>>            Move (sConnect * ";" + CS_SQLIniTrustedKeyword + "=Yes") to sConnect
82120>>>>>>>>>        End
82120>>>>>>>>>>
82120>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
82121>>>>>>>>>            Move (sConnect * ";" + CS_SQLIniUIDKeyword + "=" + sUserID * ";" + CS_SQLIniPWDKeyword + "=" + sPassword) to sConnect
82122>>>>>>>>>        End
82122>>>>>>>>>>
82122>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sConnect
82123>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82124>>>>>>>>>    
82124>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
82126>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
82126>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
82126>>>>>>>>>        
82126>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
82127>>>>>>>>>        Move 0 to LastErr  // Do NOT use the Err flag, it will be set true by the login command although it is successful.
82128>>>>>>>>>        If (bTrusted = False) Begin
82130>>>>>>>>>            Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
82132>>>>>>>>>        End 
82132>>>>>>>>>>
82132>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
82133>>>>>>>>>            Login sConnectionString "" "" sDriverID
82135>>>>>>>>>        End
82135>>>>>>>>>>
82135>>>>>>>>>        Move (LastErr = 0) to bLoginSuccessful
82136>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
82137>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82138>>>>>>>>>End_Class
