82147>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDB2Driver is a cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver
82148>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
82150>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
82150>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
82150>>>>>>>>>        
82150>>>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
82151>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
82152>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Uppercase(sServer) contains "DSN")) Begin
82154>>>>>>>>>            Move ("DSN=" + sServer) to sServer
82155>>>>>>>>>        End
82155>>>>>>>>>>
82155>>>>>>>>>        Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
82157>>>>>>>>>        
82157>>>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
82158>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
82159>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82160>>>>>>>>>End_Class
