82232>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDatabaseDriver is a cObject
82233>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
82235>>>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
82237>>>>>>>>>        Property String psDriverID DATAFLEX_ID
82238>>>>>>>>>        Property Handle phoDriverSpecificObject
82239>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82240>>>>>>>>>    
82240>>>>>>>>>    Function CreateDriver Returns Handle
82242>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID
82242>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver hcDriverClass
82242>>>>>>>>>        
82242>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
82243>>>>>>>>>        Case Begin
82243>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MSSQLDRV_ID)
82245>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMSSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82246>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82247>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ODBC_DRV_ID)
82250>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateODBCDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82251>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82252>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DB2_DRV_ID)
82255>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDB2Driver)) to hcDriverClass
82256>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82257>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = SQLFLEX)
82260>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateSQLFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82261>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82262>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ORAFLEX)
82265>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateORAFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82266>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82267>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSPgSQL)
82270>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSPgSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82271>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82272>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSMySQL)
82275>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSMySQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82276>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82277>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DATAFLEX_ID)
82280>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDataFlexDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82281>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82282>>>>>>>>>            Case Else
82282>>>>>>>>>                Function_Return 0
82283>>>>>>>>>        Case End
82283>>>>>>>>>        
82283>>>>>>>>>        Get Create hcDriverClass to hoDriver
82284>>>>>>>>>        Set psDriverID of hoDriver to sDriverID
82285>>>>>>>>>        Set phoDriverSpecificObject to hoDriver
82286>>>>>>>>>        
82286>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hoDriver
82287>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82288>>>>>>>>>    
82288>>>>>>>>>    Procedure DestroyDriver
82290>>>>>>>>>        If (phoDriverSpecificObject(Self)) Begin
82292>>>>>>>>>            Send Destroy of (phoDriverSpecificObject(Self))
82293>>>>>>>>>        End
82293>>>>>>>>>>
82293>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82294>>>>>>>>>    
82294>>>>>>>>>    Function ConstructConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns String
82296>>>>>>>>>        String sConnect
82296>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver
82296>>>>>>>>>        
82296>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateDriver to hoDriver
82297>>>>>>>>>        Get ConstructConnectionString of hoDriver sServer sDatabase bTrusted sUserID sPassword to sConnect
82298>>>>>>>>>        Send DestroyDriver
82299>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sConnect
82300>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82301>>>>>>>>>    
82301>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
82303>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
82303>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver
82303>>>>>>>>>        
82303>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateDriver to hoDriver
82304>>>>>>>>>        Get DbLogin of hoDriver sConnectionString sServer sDatabase bTrusted sUserID sPassword to bLoginSuccessful
82305>>>>>>>>>        Send DestroyDriver
82306>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
82307>>>>>>>>>    End_Function 
82308>>>>>>>>>    
82308>>>>>>>>>End_Class
