82345>>>>>>>    // *** Generalized messages to Get & Set values of the ini file.
82345>>>>>>>    // Sets a value in the program's ini file (write)
82345>>>>>>>    // Pass a section name, the value name parameter and the value itself to be written.
82345>>>>>>>    Procedure Set IniFileValue String sSection String sValueName String sValue
82347>>>>>>>        String sIniFile sPath
82347>>>>>>>
82347>>>>>>>        Get psIniFilePath to sPath   
82348>>>>>>>        Get psIniFileName to sIniFile
82349>>>>>>>        Move (sPath + sIniFile) to sIniFile
82350>>>>>>>        Set psFileName to sIniFile
82351>>>>>>>        Send WriteString sSection sValueName sValue
82352>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82353>>>>>>>
82353>>>>>>>    // Get a value from program's ini-file (read)
82353>>>>>>>    // Pass a section name and the name of the value parameter & a default value.
82353>>>>>>>    // Returns the value
82353>>>>>>>    Function IniFileValue String sSection String sValueName String sDefaultValue Returns String
82355>>>>>>>        String sValue sIniFile sPath
