82355>>>>>>>        Get psIniFilePath to sPath
82356>>>>>>>        Get psIniFileName to sIniFile
82357>>>>>>>        Move (sPath + sIniFile) to sIniFile
82358>>>>>>>        Set psFileName to sIniFile
82359>>>>>>>        Get ReadString sSection sValueName sDefaultValue to sValue
82360>>>>>>>
82360>>>>>>>        Function_Return sValue
82361>>>>>>>    End_Function                     
