82865>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection 
82865>>>>>
82865>>>>>        Forward Send End_Construct_Object
82867>>>>>
82867>>>>>        // Now is the time to read and apply SQL connection settings.
82867>>>>>        Get SetupSQLConnection True to SQLConnection   
