83001>>>>>    // Note: If the psDriverID + other connection properties are to be changed,
83001>>>>>    //       the psDriverID *must* be the first property that is changed!
83001>>>>>    //       Otherwise errors might be raised by the driver when e.g. the format
83001>>>>>    //       for a connection string has the wrong format for that driver.
