83400>>>>>    // This is needed when e.g. the connection id we have specified in the program code
83400>>>>>    // also exists in e.g. the MSSQLDRV.ini file (can either be local in the Data folder
83400>>>>>    // or the one in the DataFlex Bin folder.)
83400>>>>>    // We then need to delete the current one before creating a new one.
83400>>>>>    // This is because the parameters may differ between the program code and the
83400>>>>>    // MSSQLDRV.ini file in a deployed environment. Also DataFlex will generate an error
83400>>>>>    // when one tries to create a Connection ID that already exists.
83400>>>>>    Procedure RemoveExistingConnectionID String sDriverID String sConnectionID
83402>>>>>        Integer iResult iDriver iNumConn iConn
83402>>>>>        Handle hoCLI
