83404>>>>>            Procedure_Return
83405>>>>>        End                 
83405>>>>>>
83405>>>>>        
83405>>>>>        Move 0 to iResult
83406>>>>>        Get Create U_cCLIHandler to hoCLI
83407>>>>>        If (hoCLI <> 0) Begin
83409>>>>>            Set psDriverID of hoCLI to sDriverID   
83410>>>>>            Get DriverIndex sDriverID to iDriver
83411>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_NUMBER_CONNECTION_IDS of iDriver to iNumConn 
83414>>>>>            Decrement iNumConn
83415>>>>>            For iConn from 0 to iNumConn
83421>>>>>>
83421>>>>>                Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_CONNECTION_ID of iDriver iConn to sID
83424>>>>>                If (Uppercase(sID) = Uppercase(sConnectionID)) Begin
83426>>>>>                    Get DeleteConnectionID of hoCLI sConnectionID -1 to iResult
83427>>>>>                End
83427>>>>>>
83427>>>>>            Loop
83428>>>>>>
83428>>>>>            Send Destroy of hoCLI
83429>>>>>        End
83429>>>>>>
83429>>>>>    
83429>>>>>    End_Procedure   
