83454>>>>>                    Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_CONNECTION_ID of iDriver iConn              to SQLConnection.sConnectionID  // For completeness only...
83457>>>>>                    Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_CONNECTION_ID_STRING of iDriver iConn       to sConnectionString
83460>>>>>                    Move sConnectionString                                              to SQLConnection.sConnectionString 
83461>>>>>                    Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_CONNECTION_ID_OPTIONS of iDriver iConn      to SQLConnection.bSilentLogin
83464>>>>>                    Get ParseKeyWord sConnectionString (CS_SQLIniServerKeyword + "=")   to SQLConnection.sServer
83465>>>>>                    Get ParseKeyWord sConnectionString (CS_SQLIniDatabaseKeyword + "=") to SQLConnection.sDatabase
83466>>>>>                    Get ParseKeyWord sConnectionString (CS_SQLIniUIDKeyword + "=")      to SQLConnection.sUserID
83467>>>>>                    Get ParseKeyWord sConnectionString (CS_SQLIniPWDKeyword + "=")      to SQLConnection.sPassword
83468>>>>>                    
