83666>>>>>
83666>>>>>    // Sample sConnString: "SERVER=(local)\SQLEXPRESS;UID=dbuser;PWD=secret;DATABASE=OrderEntry;, 0"
83666>>>>>    // Pass a complete driver connection string
83666>>>>>    // Returns the following as a struct:
83666>>>>>    //   sServer, sDatabase, sUser, sPassword & True if Trusted_Connection is used.
83666>>>>>    // Finally also returns a boolean TRUE if trusted_connection=yes, else false is returned. 
83666>>>>>    //
83666>>>>>    Function DeComposeConnectionString String sDriverID String sConnectionString Returns tSQLConnection
83668>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection
83668>>>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection
