83983>>>    Function SqlTableCreate Integer hTable Returns Boolean
83985>>>        String sTableName sSQLString sPath sVal sCreateTable sDriverID
83985>>>        Integer iRetval iDbType                      
83985>>>        Boolean bExists bOK
