84155>>>    // The fourth & fifth arguments are optional, depending on the iDataType
84155>>>    // passed. For e.g. a DF_ASCII the iLen must be passed.                     // Optional: // Optional:  
84155>>>    Function SqlColumnChange Handle hTable String sColumnName Integer iDataType Integer iLen Integer iDec Returns Boolean
84157>>>        Integer iColumn iDbType iLength iDecimals
