86203>>>        Get phoMSSQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
86204>>>        Send Delete_Data    of hoSQLHandler
86205>>>        Get pSQLConnection  of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to SQLConnection
86206>>>
86206>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
86207>>>        Get EnumerateDatabases of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword to iSize
86208>>>        Decrement iSize
86209>>>
86209>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
86215>>>>
