86351>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
86352>>>
86352>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
86353>>>
86353>>>        Repeat
86353>>>>
86353>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
86354>>>            If (Trim(sDataSource) <> "" and not(sDataSource contains "*.")) Begin
