86663>>>    Procedure ApiTableConvertALLToSQL 
86665>>>        Integer[] iTablesArray                 
86666>>>        Integer iSize iCount                     
86666>>>        Boolean bUseConnectionID bToANSI bRecnum bCopyData bOK
86666>>>        String sDriverID
86666>>>        
86666>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID   
86667>>>        Get pbUseConnectionID to bUseConnectionID
86668>>>        Get pbToANSI          to bToANSI
86669>>>        Get pbRecnum          to bRecnum
86670>>>        Get pbCopyData        to bCopyData
86671>>>        
86671>>>        Get _AllTablesToConvert to iTablesArray
86672>>>        Move (SizeOfArray(iTablesArray)) to iSize
86673>>>        Decrement iSize
86674>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
86680>>>>
86680>>>            Get ApiTableConvertToSQL_Ex iTablesArray[iCount] sDriverID bUseConnectionID bToANSI bRecnum bCopyData to bOK
86681>>>        Loop
86682>>>>
86682>>>    
