87264>>>    // Removes the passed table name completely from disk, filelist (& Sql Server if an Sql-driver)
87264>>>    Function ApiTableRemove Handle hTable Returns Boolean
87266>>>        String sTableName sDriverID  
87266>>>        Boolean bOk     
87266>>>        String sDataPath
87266>>>        
87266>>>        Get AutoConnectionIDLogin to bOK
87267>>>        Move False to Err 
