87480>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FIELD_PRECISION of hTable iOld to iPrecision
87483>>>        End
87483>>>>
87483>>>        Move False to Err
87484>>>    
87484>>>        Structure_Start hTable  
87485>>>            Delete_Field hTable iOld
87486>>>            Create_Field hTable At iNew
87487>>>            Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of hTable iNew to sColumn
87490>>>            Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_TYPE of hTable iNew to iType
87493>>>    
