87530>>>    // Renames a field for the passed table number & old field name & new field name
87530>>>    // Returns True if no errors occured.
87530>>>    // Sample usage:
87530>>>    //   Get ColumnRename Quote.File_Number "ID#" "ID" to bOK
87530>>>    Function ApiColumnRename Integer hTable String sOldFieldName String sNewFieldName Returns Boolean
87532>>>        Integer iField
87532>>>        Boolean bOK
87532>>>        
87532>>>        Get AutoConnectionIDLogin to bOK
87533>>>        Move False to Err
87534>>>        Open hTable Mode DF_EXCLUSIVE
87536>>>    
87536>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_CANT_FIND_FIELD
87537>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_DUPLICATE_FIELDNAME
87538>>>        Structure_Start hTable
87539>>>            Field_Map hTable sOldFieldName to iField
87541>>>            If (iField > 0) Begin
87543>>>                Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of hTable iField to sNewFieldName
87546>>>            End
87546>>>>
87546>>>            Else Begin
87547>>>                Move 0 to LastErr
87548>>>                Move False to Err
87549>>>            End
87549>>>>
87549>>>        Structure_End hTable
87551>>>    
87551>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_CANT_FIND_FIELD
87552>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_DUPLICATE_FIELDNAME
87553>>>        
87553>>>        Function_Return (Err = False)
87554>>>    End_Function
