89927>>>        Handle ho
89927>>>        Integer iDriverIndex
89927>>>        
89927>>>        Get DriverIndex MSSQLDRV_ID to iDriverIndex
89928>>>        
89928>>>        Function_Return (iDriverIndex <> 0)
89929>>>    End_Function
