89930>>>    // Similar to _SqlCheckCurrentDriver but generates no error and it doesn't 
89930>>>    // attempt to load the driver.
89930>>>    // Returns true if the passed driver is SQL based.        
89930>>>    Function IsSQLDriver String sDriverID Returns Boolean
89932>>>        Boolean bOK                         
