89969>>>    Function psDataPathFirstPart Returns String
89971>>>        String sDataPath
89971>>>        Integer iCount
89971>>>        
89971>>>        Get psDataPath of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) to sDataPath
89972>>>        Get CountOfPaths of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) sDataPath to iCount
89973>>>        If (iCount > 1) Begin
89975>>>            Get PathAtIndex of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) sDataPath 1 to sDataPath    
89976>>>        End             
89976>>>>
89976>>>        If (sDataPath <> "") Begin
89978>>>            Get vFolderFormat sDataPath to sDataPath
89979>>>        End
89979>>>>
89979>>>        
89979>>>        Function_Return sDataPath
89980>>>    End_Function
