91209>>>
91209>>>// This provides a quick and simple way to create an about package for a program.
91209>>>// You need to create a message inside you client area called Activate_About.
91209>>>// Within this message you should send the message DoAbout passing needed
91209>>>// string information.
91209>>>//
91209>>>//       Procedure Activate_About
91209>>>//           Send DoAbout sTitle sVersion sCopyright sAuthor sBitmap
91209>>>//       End_Procedure
91209>>>//    where: sTitle =     Name of application. If none provided, uses caption
91209>>>//                        bar title
91209>>>//           sVersion   = Version Line. If none provided, will be blank
91209>>>//           sCopyRight = Copyright Line. If none provided, will be blank
91209>>>//           sAuthor    = Author name, blank if none provided
91209>>>//           sBitMap    = Bitmap logo. If none provided, standard VDF bitmap
91209>>>//                        is used.
91209>>>// It is expected that you will place this in your own object package. For
91209>>>// example an order about package may look like this:
91209>>>//
91209>>>//   // OrderAbout.pkg
91209>>>//   Use StdAbout.pkg
91209>>>//   Procedure Activate_About
91209>>>//      String sTitle sCopyright sVersion sAuthor
91209>>>//      Move "My Order Entry System" to sTitle
91209>>>//      Move "Version 2.1" to sVersion
91209>>>//      Move "Copyright 1997, Super Software Inc." to sCopyright
91209>>>//      Move "John Smith"  to sAuthor
91209>>>//      Send DoAbout sTitle sVersion sCopyright sAuthor ""
91209>>>//   end_procedure
91209>>>//   // end of file.
91209>>>
91209>>>Use DfAbout.pkg
Including file: DfAbout.pkg    (C:\Projects\DF18\DbUpdateFramework\AppSrc\DfAbout.pkg)
91209>>>>>//************************************************************************
91209>>>>>// Confidential Trade Secret.
