91209>>>>>//
91209>>>>>// $File name  : DfAbout.pkg
91209>>>>>// $File title : About class support
91209>>>>>// Notice      :
91209>>>>>// $Author(s)  : Vincent Oorsprong, Ken Ross
91209>>>>>//
91209>>>>>// $Rev History
91209>>>>>//
91209>>>>>// NGS 08/16/2013 Improved by using a cRichEdit object were the params gets added to.
91209>>>>>//                The objects that previously were popupated with values from the params,
91209>>>>>//                and their corresponding "Procedure Set..." messages, were removed as
91209>>>>>//                the edit object is used instead.
91209>>>>>//                The number of params to the DoAbout procedure was increased to ten, so
91209>>>>>//                it is easier to add whatever extra text strings needed/wanted.
91209>>>>>//                The StdAbout.pkg was also changed for this to work. It allows for an extra
91209>>>>>//                five new params to be passed, but these new params are all optional.
91209>>>>>//                So the interface will work exactly as before - if no extra parameters are passed.
91209>>>>>//                Also added an extra bitmap object to show the "Powered By Visual DataFlex" logo, in
91209>>>>>//                the lower left corner of the About object, beneath the "main" About bitmap.
91209>>>>>//                Note: It is assumed that the bitmap "PoweredByVisualDataFlex.bmp" exists.
91209>>>>>//                The background was changed to clWhite for easier usage of bitmaps. Just set the background
91209>>>>>//                color of your bitmap to white and the bitmap will not look jagged.
91209>>>>>//                If an Internet address is passed as one of the params, it will be underlined and clickable.
91209>>>>>//                An e-mail address can also be passed; e.g. "E-mail: mailto:mail@myemailaccount.com" and will
91209>>>>>//                also be clickable.
91209>>>>>// VOO 02/22/2012 Replaced obsolete code, improved Network_User_Name by asking
91209>>>>>//                Windows for the size first.
91209>>>>>// VOO 07/25/2003 Removed OnResize procedure for sysinfo dialog. Replaced logic
91209>>>>>//                with anchor technique. Removed unnessary property in the
91209>>>>>//                sysinfo dialog. Changed the size Of the about & sysinfo dialog
91209>>>>>//                object To better look in Windows XP. Repositioned the close
91209>>>>>//                button in the sysinfo dialog To line up with the display area
91209>>>>>//                Replaced obsolete code and techniques. Removed dead code.
91209>>>>>// JJT 10/23/2001 removed all ghoworkspace support. Uses app object or nothing
91209>>>>>// SWB 07/19/01   Added support Of the Application object in preference to
91209>>>>>//                the global Workspace object, if it is present
91209>>>>>// JJT 11/05/98   Added version information
91209>>>>>// VOO 29/10/98   Replaced the GetFreeSystemResources for the Win32 variant
91209>>>>>// JJT 7/31/97    Registered Enumerate Workspace so dfabout can exist without
91209>>>>>//                workspace package.
91209>>>>>// JJT 6/27/97    Turned the sysinfo objects into classes so the AboutDialog
91209>>>>>//                class can create this object.
91209>>>>>//                Cleaned up the interface (used correct classes and messages)
91209>>>>>//                Added workspace reporting support To sys-info.
91209>>>>>//                Turned off wrapping in the sys-info editor.
91209>>>>>// KR  ??/??/96   File created
91209>>>>>//************************************************************************
