91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>// Protected Messages:
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//        These messages invoke the Window's help system and are not
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//        directly sent by outside objects. They are sent by public
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//        "view_xxx" messages and might be used if you are creating
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//        a sub-class of an object-class.
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Procedure Exec_System_Context_Help  integer Context_id
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Procedure Exec_System_Help          string  Keyword
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Procedure Exec_Context_Help         string  Context
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Functions for converting DF help IDs to windows Help Ids
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//        Any of these can return either a string or an integer.
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Function System_Help_Context_id Integer ID Returns String
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           Convert a DF help context id into a windows id. By default,
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           just return the same value (a one to one match). This is called
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           by View_Context_id_help and View_Context_Help
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Function System_Help_File_Id Integer File# Integer Field# Returns String
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           Convert file and field into a help id. By default it returns the
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           file#. Called by View_File_Help.
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//    Function System_Help_Error_id Integer Id Returns String
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           Convert an error message into an ID. Right now it returns the
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           the general error context id property, Help_id_errors. This
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           will invoke general error help. If you want error support at the
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           error# level you will have to determine the program to help
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           interface yourself. Errors have a very large range and it is
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           therefore hard to come up with an automatic numbering scheme.
91495>>>>>>>>>>>//           Called by View_Error_Help.
91495>>>>>>>>>>>
91495>>>>>>>>>>>
91495>>>>>>>>>>>Use Windows.pkg
91495>>>>>>>>>>>Use WinHlp.pkg // low level help call to windows API provides global message gDoWinHelp
91495>>>>>>>>>>>Use HelpSystemConstants.pkg // constants used by help system
91495>>>>>>>>>>>
91495>>>>>>>>>>>Register_Function phoWorkspace Returns Handle
91495>>>>>>>>>>>Register_function peHelpType  returns integer
