91741>>>>>                Move "Workspace Config Filename:" to sText
91742>>>>>                Get psWorkspaceWSFile of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) to sWorkspaceWSFile
91743>>>>>                Move (sText * sWorkspaceWSFile) to sText
91744>>>>>            End
91744>>>>>>
91744>>>>>        End
91744>>>>>>
91744>>>>>        Send AppendText sText
91745>>>>>        Send AppendText (character(10))
91746>>>>>    End_Procedure
