92076>>>>>    //****************************************************************************
92076>>>>>    // $Module type: PROCEDURE
92076>>>>>    // $Module name: Add_Focus
92076>>>>>    // $Author     : VOO
92076>>>>>    // Created     : 24-09-96 @ 19:43
92076>>>>>    //
92076>>>>>    // Description
92076>>>>>    //    During activation we will remove the old information and add the newly
92076>>>>>    //    found systeminformation
92076>>>>>    //
92076>>>>>    // $Rev History
92076>>>>>    //    24-09-96  Module header created
92076>>>>>    //****************************************************************************
92076>>>>>    Procedure Add_Focus Integer hoRoot
92078>>>>>        Forward Send Add_Focus hoRoot
92080>>>>>
92080>>>>>        Send Delete_Data
92081>>>>>
92081>>>>>        Set Changed_State To False
92082>>>>>        Set Read_Only_State To True
92083>>>>>
92083>>>>>        Send Show_Registration
92084>>>>>        Send Show_Drivers
92085>>>>>        Send AppendTextLn ""
92086>>>>>
92086>>>>>        Send Show_ServicePack
92087>>>>>        If (ghoApplication <> 0) Begin
92089>>>>>            Send Show_WorkSpaceInformation
92090>>>>>            Send Show_HelpFile
92091>>>>>            Send AppendTextLn ""
92092>>>>>        End
92092>>>>>>
92092>>>>>        Else Begin
92093>>>>>            Send AppendTextLn ""
92094>>>>>        End
92094>>>>>>
92094>>>>>
92094>>>>>        If (ghoConnection <> 0) Begin
92096>>>>>            Send Show_ConnectionIdInformation
92097>>>>>        End
92097>>>>>>
92097>>>>>        
92097>>>>>        Send Show_Current_User
92098>>>>>        Send Show_Windows_Directory
92099>>>>>        Send Show_Current_Directory
92100>>>>>
92100>>>>>        // This is already shown in the workspace details,
92100>>>>>        // unless no workspace object is present:
92100>>>>>        If (ghoApplication = 0) Begin
92102>>>>>            Send Show_Filelist_Name
92103>>>>>        End
92103>>>>>>
92103>>>>>
92103>>>>>        If (ghoApplication <> 0) Begin
92105>>>>>            Send AppendTextLn ""
